<p>
<seg id=1> In Yemen, freed Western tourists said the kidnappers hid behind them as shields during the army's rescue operation. </seg>
<seg id=2> Four tourists were killed in Tuesday's gun fight. Twelve people managed to escape. </seg>
<seg id=3> The Yemeni government said the army launched the attack when it was obvious that the kidnappers would kill the hostages. </seg>
<seg id=4> However, some freed tourists said the gun fight broke out after the start of the rescue operation. </seg>
</p>
